title: FastTracker music: Anvil - Dream Complex II (GUS PnP clone)
description:
"Dream Complex II" (2003), a remake megamix of Elwood's works by Anvil (Hannu Koskinen). Original tracks by Elwood of course.
Amiga art "The Funk Phenomenon" by Critikill/Brainstorm^Rebels^SWEET16, 4th at Evoke 2023.

Open Cubic Player 2.6.0pre6 and Gravis Ultrasound PnP clone hardware mixing (InterWave).
